title: Disney Shorts - ALL OF THEM
description:
Here is almost every Disney animated short ever created. There are maybe 20-30 missing from this collection. Every one of these is excellent quality, the vast majority of them are DVD rips. Most are in AVI format, some are MPG. Each one is in English, with NO subtitles.

Enjoy, and please seed!!!
